Like a [[Measure]] but where additivity is replaced by sub-additivity, that is:

$$\mu(\bigcup\limits_{i=1}^{\infty} E_i) \leq \sum\limits_{i=1}^{\infty} \mu(E_i)$$ for any collection $$E_1, E_2, ... \in \mathcal{A}$$ of mutually disjoint sets.

